"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua"									"死神镰刀"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_Description"						"眩晕一名敌人，然后造成基于他当前损失生命值的伤害。瘟疫法师击杀敌方英雄后将永久获得生命和魔法恢复。<font color='#70EA72'>成功斩杀时，目标每剩余1%%的生命值，就返还%mana_back%%%的魔法消耗和%cd_back%%%的剩余冷却时间。</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_Lore"							"空气中充斥的死亡和苦难增强了瘟疫法师的瘟疫魔法。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_Note0"							"伤害在眩晕结束后结算。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_damage_per_health"				"每点损失生命值造成伤害："
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_stun_duration"					"眩晕时间："
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_hp_per_kill"						"生命恢复："
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_mana_per_kill"					"魔法恢复："
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_AbilityCastRange"					"施法距离："
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_stack"					"死神镰刀"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_stack_Description" "因击杀永久获得%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_HEALTH_REGEN_CONSTANT%点/秒生命恢复和%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MANA_REGEN_CONSTANT%点/秒魔法恢复。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua"							"熠熠生辉"
"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_Lore"						"由于接触不到光之子的光芒，力量无法恢复而不断衰退，但维罗拉还是从每场战斗中存在的混沌里创造了秩序，使自身和盟友得到休整。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_Description"				"%attack_count%次攻击后，破晓辰星提升了力量，她的下一次攻击会造成致命一击，并治疗她附近%heal_radius%范围内所有友方英雄，治疗量为攻击伤害的一定百分比。攻击小兵和野怪产生的治疗量有所减少。对友军的治疗量为%allied_healing_pct%%%。<font color='#70EA72'>在白天，致命一击伤害和治疗量还会提高%bonus_damage_daytime%%%。</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_Note0"						"熠熠生辉的治疗效果被认定为吸血，可以通过吸血增强效果获得提升。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_bonus_damage"				"%致命一击伤害："
"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_heal_pct"					"%攻击英雄治疗量："
"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_heal_from_creeps"			"%攻击普通单位治疗减少："
"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_attack_count"				"所需攻击次数："
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua"							"熠熠生辉"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_Description"				"因熠熠生辉而增强了力量"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua"						"神行太保"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_Lore"					"英雄们只要留心观察裂魂人在战场上的支配地位，就能提高他们的速度与力量。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_Description"			"根据裂魂人的移动速度提高他的攻击力。每当一个目标死于裂魂人的攻击，他都会永久获得移动速度。裂魂人可以突破移动速度上限。每次学习都会提升神行太保的叠加层数。<br><br>基础移动速度不计算在内。<br>如果英雄的当前移动速度低于他的基础移动速度，神行太保将不会提供攻击力加成。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_movespeed_damage_pct"	"%移动速度转化为攻击力比例："
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_bonus_movespeed_per_kill"	"击杀英雄获得移动速度："
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_bonus_movespeed_per_kill_creep"			"击杀非英雄获得移动速度："
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_basic_stack"			"每次学习提升叠加层数："
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua"							"神行太保"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_Description"				"移动速度提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT%点"

